<mjml lang="en">
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title>Scaleway newsletter</mj-title>
    <mj-font name="Poppins" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" />
    <mj-font name="Asap" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Asap:wght@400;700&display=swap" />
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body>
    <mj-hero mode="fixed-height" height="400px" background-url="Header.svg" background-color="#4F0599">
      <mj-image alt="scaleway logo" width="180px" href="https://www.scaleway.com/fr/" src="Scaleway-Logo-Purple-RGB 1.svg" />
    </mj-hero>

    <mj-section background-color="#FFFFFF">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" font-weight="700" font-size="40px" line-height="35px" font-family="Poppins" color="#4F0599">
          Unlock a new experience
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-weight="700" font-size="21px" line-height="32px" color="#AE5DF6">
          <div style="max-width: 500px; margin: auto;">
            Link your Dedibox dedicated servers to the Scaleway console
          </div>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button height="16px" background-color="#22C8A2" color="#FFFFFF" border-radius="4px" width="200px" font-weight="700" font-size="14px" line-height="20px" font-family="Asap">
          Get started
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding-top="0" background-color="#FFFFFF">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" font-family="Asap" font-weight="400" font-size="14px" line-height="24px" color="#4A4F62">
          We now offer you the possibility to link all your Dedibox to the
          Scaleway console.
          <b>
            The link is free,
          </b>
          and will bring you new opportunities. Manage all your Dedibox
          servers within a powerful easy-to-use console. Discover Scaleway cloud
          products and create a powerful environement, all at the same place!
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#FFFFFF">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" align="left" font-family="Poppins" font-weight="700" font-size="12px" line-height="32px" color="#AE5DF6">
          What do we link?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-top="0" align="left" font-family="Poppins" font-weight="700" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" color="#4F0599">
          All your Dedibox servers, services and options
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-top="0" align="left" font-family="Asap" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" color="#4A4F62">
          Once the process is complete, you will be able to manage all your
          ressources from the Scaleway Console.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="240px" alt="dedibox-servers" src="imgList@2x.png" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#FFFFFF" direction="rtl">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" align="left" font-weight="700" font-size="12px" line-height="32px" font-family="Poppins" color="#AE5DF6">
          Why should you do it?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-top="0" align="left" font-weight="700" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" font-family="Poppins" color="#4F0599">
          Discover the best console experience on the market
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-top="0" align="left" font-family="Asap" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" color="#4A4F62">
          Get the full power of Scaleway cloud products within a blazing fast
          and smooth user interface.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="240px" alt="console experience" src="imgConsole@2x.png" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#FFFFFF">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" align="left" font-weight="700" font-size="12px" line-height="32px" font-family="Poppins" color="#AE5DF6">
          Explore new opportunities
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-top="0" align="left" font-weight="700" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" font-family="Poppins" color="#4F0599">
          Get a €100 voucher to discover new products
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-top="0" align="left" font-family="Asap" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" color="#4A4F62">
          Even if you already have a Scaleway Elements account! Discover the new
          Dedibox dashboard and take some time to check out our cloud products
          and features, like Instances, Object Storage and much more.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image width="240px" alt="100 voucher" src="imgVoucher@2x.png" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#FFFFFF">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button height="16px" background-color="#22C8A2" color="#FFFFFF" border-radius="4px" width="200px" font-weight="700" font-size="14px" line-height="20px" font-family="Asap">
          Get started
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#4F0599" padding="0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image padding="0" alt="background purple-cloud" src="Footer.svg" container-background-color="#FFFFFF" />
        <mj-text align="center" font-weight="700" font-size="25px" line-height="35px" font-family="Poppins" color="#FFFFFF">
          <mj-button href="https://link-dedibox.scaleway.com/ " style="cursor: pointer">
            F.A.Q
          </mj-button>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" font-weight="600" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" font-family="Poppins" color="#FFFFFF">
          Q. What exactly is going to be linked?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" font-family="Asap" color="#FFFFFF">
          We link all of your dedicated resources in a brand new interface! Web
          domains and web hosting will not be linked at this stage, but will
          remain accessible in your current console.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#D4DAE7" />

        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" font-weight="600" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" font-family="Poppins" color="#FFFFFF">
          Q. How long will it take?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" font-family="Asap" color="#FFFFFF">
          The process is just a 5 minute link. The time for you to review your
          account information and voilà!
        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#D4DAE7" />

        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" font-weight="600" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" font-family="Poppins" color="#FFFFFF">
          Q. Will it replace the current console?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" font-family="Asap" color="#FFFFFF">
          Some operations are not yet available in the Scaleway console, but you
          will soon be able to do everything you need. In the meantime, your
          current console remains available.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#D4DAE7" />

        <mj-text padding-bottom="0" font-weight="600" font-size="16px" line-height="24px" font-family="Poppins" color="#FFFFFF">
          Q. Can I still use the Dedibox console online.net after the upgrade?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left" font-weight="400" font-size="12px" line-height="18px" font-family="Asap" color="#FFFFFF">
          Yes you can.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#D4DAE7" />

        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        <mj-button height="16px" background-color="#22C8A2" color="#FFFFFF" border-radius="4px" width="200px" font-weight="700" font-size="14px" line-height="20px" font-family="Asap">
          Get started
        </mj-button>
        <mj-image alt="background purple-cloud" width="200px" href="https://www.scaleway.com/fr/" src="Scaleway-Logo-Purple-RGB 1.svg" />

      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>;